OL,3,CCall for action after 'devastating'
OL,4,Crise in drink deaths
OL,6,FSome 8,274 people in England lost
OL,7,Ftheir lives to alcohol in 2023, the
OL,8,FAHA said, but this is just the "tip of
OL,9,Fthe iceberg" as there will have been
OL,10,Fmany more deaths where alcohol was a
OL,11,Fcontributing factor.
OL,13,FThe groups praised health officials in
OL,14,FScotland for the "life-saving" minimum
OL,15,Funit pricing (MUP) scheme but said
OL,16,Fthat "inaction across the border has
OL,17,Fled English deaths to spiral".
