OL,4,Crise in drink deaths
OL,6,FIn March 2020, the previous government
OL,7,Fsaid there were "no plans for the
OL,8,Fintroduction of MUP in England"
OL,9,Falthough it would continue to monitor
OL,10,Fthe progress of the initiative in
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,FAnd in October this year, when asked
OL,14,Fwhether the current Government had any
OL,15,Fplans to introduce minimum pricing for
OL,16,Falcohol, Home Office minister Dame
OL,17,FDiana Johnson said: "We are continuing
OL,18,Fto work closely across government to
OL,19,Fbetter understand what can be done to
OL,20,Faddress the drivers of alcohol-related
OL,21,Fharms."
