OL,6,FLord Darzi's hard-hitting review into
OL,7,Fthe NHS in England highlights how
OL,8,Falcohol is "becoming more affordable
OL,9,Fover time, and deaths are rising at an
OL,10,Falarming rate".
OL,12,FThe AHA letter, seen by the PA news
OL,13,Fagency, adds that the "alcohol harm
OL,14,Fcrisis" will only escalate if action
OL,15,Fis not taken to reduce alcohol
OL,16,Fconsumption.
OL,18,F"Deaths caused solely by alcohol have
OL,19,Fincreased by a catastrophic 42% since
OL,20,F2019," the letter states.
