OL,4,Crise in drink deaths
OL,6,F"This number can be seen as the tip of
OL,7,Fthe iceberg as it reflects deaths
OL,8,Fwholly attributable to alcohol and not
OL,9,Fthose where alcohol was a contributing
OL,10,Ffactor, a figure likely to be three
OL,11,Ftimes higher."
OL,13,FThe letter highlights that there are
OL,14,Falmost 950,000 hospital admissions in
OL,15,FEngland each year are related to
OL,16,Falcohol.
