OL,6,FIt adds: "Evidence from Scotland has
OL,7,Fclearly demonstrated how policies such
OL,8,Fas minimum unit pricing (MUP) have
OL,9,Fsaved lives, while inaction across the
OL,10,Fborder has led English deaths to
OL,11,Fspiral."
OL,13,FThe authors conclude: "Left unchecked,
OL,14,Fthe alcohol harm crisis will only
OL,15,Fescalate further, placing an ever-
OL,16,Fgreater burden on our healthcare
OL,17,Fsystem, economy and society. We know
OL,18,Fwhat works, and now is the time to
OL,19,Fact."
