OL,6,FProfessor Sir Ian Gilmore, chair of
OL,7,Fthe AHA, said: "These new statistics
OL,8,Fare a stark reminder of the
OL,9,Fdevastating impact alcohol takes on
OL,10,Four society, not just in lives lost
OL,11,Fbut in the shattered families and
OL,12,Fcommunities left behind.
OL,14,F"Each of the 8,274 deaths in 2023
OL,15,Frepresents a life cut tragically
OL,16,Fshort, a loved one whose absence
OL,17,Fleaves a void that can never be filled.
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU
