OL,4,Crise in drink deaths
OL,6,F"Alcohol-related harm does not occur
OL,7,Fin isolation. It ripples through
OL,8,Ffamilies, often leaving children to
OL,9,Fbear the brunt of grief and trauma.
OL,11,F"The devastating rise in alcohol
OL,12,Fdeaths should serve as an alarm for
OL,13,Fthe new government to act with
OL,14,Furgency."
OL,16,FHe added: "We have the evidence, and
OL,17,Fwe know the solutions. Now is the
OL,18,Fmoment to show that we value human
OL,19,Flives over profit.
