OL,6,F"Without bold, decisive action, these
OL,7,Fpreventable deaths will continue to
OL,8,Fclimb. Addressing alcohol harm must be
OL,9,Fa top public health priority in 2025,
OL,10,Fand it requires a cross-government
OL,11,Feffort to turn the tide on this public
OL,12,Fhealth crisis."
OL,14,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,15,FCare has been approached for comment.
